The paper deals with the problem of topology recognition in anonymous networks, which is a topic in distributed computing. The use of advice to aid in the recognition process suggests a focus on algorithm design and analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
